Install heroku gem:

Add following to Gemfile as on heroku production database working and it's adapter is postgressserver:

  # To enable features such as static asset serving and logging on Heroku,

Please add rails_12factor gem to your Gemfile.

  group :production do

    gem 'pg'

    gem 'rails_12factor'

  end

=====================================================================
 FOR DEPOLYING APP ON HEROKU :
 -----------------------------
   gem install heroku --no-ri --no-rdoc

   heroku create sampleapp
                  (sample app is application name on heroku / will ask heroku account login and create app overthere.)
                   if (sampleapp) app name not specified it will pick random name that you can further rename.

   git remote add heroku git@github.com:rah00l/sports.git

   git push heroku master
  

  git push heroku for_heroku:master (if your code is on any other branch other than master)

=====================================================================
   Application specific ::

   heroku  rake sunspot:solr:start

   heroku rake sunspot:reindex

   heroku rake db:migrate db:seed
=====================================================================
Few Common heroku commands
heroku create (will ask heroku account login and create app overthere.)

To run migrations
heroku run rake db:migrate
heroku run rake db:seed
You can rename an app at any time with the heroku apps:rename command

heroku apps:rename newname (it's change name of app and subdomain)

To check remote repository list:

   git remote -v

run migrations

    heroku run rake db:migrate

    heroku run rake db:seed

To add repo.

    git remote add heroku git@heroku.com:balanced-budget.git

To remove remote:

    git remote rm heroku

To verify logs:

    heroku logs

  To go into heroku application console:

    heroku run bash

To get list of all apps on heroku 

heroku apps

Questions - If you have an existing app on Heroku and you are getting this no app specified message, you can correct it by running this on your local terminal: 

      Issue  - Error : Error: No app specified

  Answer -   

                 heroku apps

                 heroku git:remote -a frozen-fortress-41691

  